CARD MEMORY GAME


ğŸƒ Overview

-The Card Matching Game is a fun memory-based game where players flip over cards to find matching pairs. 
-The goal is to match all pairs of cards with as few moves as possible. This project is built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.


HOW TO play


Click on a card to flip it over and reveal its icon.
Flip a second card to find a match.
If the cards match, they remain flipped; otherwise, they flip back.
Match all the pairs to win the game.
Use the Restart button to shuffle the cards and start over.


TECHNOLOGIES USED

HTML: Structure of the game board and buttons.
CSS: Styling and layout, including animations and responsive design.
JavaScript: Game logic, card shuffling, and event handling.




